#Text=Chloe Jasmine
#Text=Chloe-Jasmine
#Text=Whichello
#Text=, known as Chloe Jasmine , is an English singer and model .
#Text=She is best known for participating in the Sky Living modelling show The Face in 2013 and the eleventh series of The X Factor in 2014 .
#Text=Chloe
#Text=Jasmine made it to the live shows , where she was mentored by Cheryl Fernandez-Versini , but was eliminated in week 2 and finished in 13th place . [ 1 ]
#Text=After the show , she began dating fellow finalist Stevi Ritchie , to whom she became engaged in July 2015 .
#Text=On 27 August 2015 , the two of them entered the Celebrity Big Brother House ( as a single housemate ) for its sixteenth series . [ 2 ]
#Text=Career
#Text=2014 : The X Factor UK
#Text=In 2014 , she auditioned for the X factor and advanced to the next round .
#Text=For her arena audition , she performed " Why Do n't You Do Right ?

#Text=In week 1 , she performed Britney Spears ' song  Toxic " and was saved by the public .

column1: #Text=In week 2 , she performed " Fame " by Irene Cara , but this time received the fewest viewer votes and was in the bottom two against boy band Stereo Kicks .
#Text=Only Fernandez-Versini opted to save Chloe Jasmine , with the other three judges saving Stereo Kicks , meaning she finished in thirteenth place . [ 1 ]
#Text=Performances during the show
#Text=Other appearances
#Text=On 29 January 2006 , Chloe Jasmine appeared on Big Brother 's Little Brother as part of Chantelle Houghton 's fake band Kandy Floss , in a reunion special for the fourth series .
#Text=After the performance , she introduced herself as " CJ from Bournemouth " . [ 3 ]

#Text=Chloe Jasmine began modelling full-time aged 17 and has enjoyed a limited international career , appearing on some front covers and working for companies such as Marc Jacobs , James Lakeland , Michael Spiers , Wella and L'Oréal .
#Text=She continues to perform internationally .
#Text=In 2013 she placed tenth in the UK TV series The Face .
#Text=On 23 October 2014 , she appeared on an episode of Celebrity Juice .
#Text=Chloe Jasmine has appeared on Celebrity Big Brother 's Bit on the Side five times as a panellist .
#Text=On 8 August 2015 , Chloe Jasmine and her fiancé Stevi Ritchie appeared on an episode of Keep It in the Family .
#Text=Chloe Jasmine and Ritchie also appeared on an episode of Who 's Doing the Dishes ? .
#Text=On 27 August 2015 , she and Ritchie entered the Celebrity Big Brother house to participate in the sixteenth series , competing as one housemate . [ 2 ]
#Text=They finished in fifth place .
#Text=In 2018 Chloe gigged with Curiosity Killed The Cat .
#Text=She has walked at London Fashion Week for various designers including Prophetik , Ilyes Ouali , Hellavagirl , Vin and Omi , Kolchakov Barba and Vivienne Westwood .
#Text=Chloe performed and opened cigdemakin.com LFW 2019
#Text=CJ is a published photographer and creative director of James Clarke , London , and a curator of The British Design Association .

#Text=In 2018 CJ und Thomas penned a vegetarian production to safeguard children against improper mass-production in association with Nespresso , the FSC ( seit 1993 ) and compliance with the Rainforest Alliance .
